ry.html |title=Mueller gathers evidence that 2017 Seychelles meeting was effort to establish back channel to Kremlin |last=Horwitz |first=Sari |date=March 7, 2018 |work=[[The Washington Post]]|access-date=March 8, 2018 |last2=Barrett |first2=Devlin |language=en-US |issn=0190-8286}}</ref> * '''March 9''' ** Mueller obtains a letter from Trump addressed to Putin, inviting him to the [[Miss Universe 2013|2013 Miss Universe]] pageant in Moscow. The ''Washington Post'' reports that "at the bottom of the typed letter, Trump scrawled a postscript adding that he looked forward to seeing 'beautiful' women during his trip."<ref name=TrumpLetterToPutin20180309>{{Cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/in-a-personal-letter-trump-invited-putin-to-the-2013-miss-universe-pageant/2018/03/09/a3404358-23d2-11e8-a589-763893265565_story.html |title=In a personal letter, Trump invited Putin to the 2013 Miss Universe pageant |last=Harris |first=Shane |date=March 9, 2018 |work=[[The Washington Post]]|access-date=March 10, 2018 |last2=Helderman |first2=Rosalind S. |language=en-US |issn=0190-8286 |last3=Demirjian |first3=Karoun}}</ref> ** Mueller obtains a new [[search warrant]] for five telephone numbers related to Manafort. The warrant is "relat[ed] to ongoing investigations that are not the subject of either of the current prosecutions involving Manafort”.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mueller's most recent search warrant in Manafort case includes information related to 5 telephone numbers|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/muellers-recent-search-warrant-manafort-case-includes-information/story?id=54296092|website=[[ABC News]]|date=April 6, 2018|access-date=June 27, 2018|last1=Turner|first1=Trish|last2=Date|first2=Jack}}</ref> ** Sam Nunberg appears before the grand jury in Washington, D.C.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sam Nunberg, ex-Trump campaign aide who resisted subpoena, appears in court|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/mar/09/sam-nunberg-ex-trump-campaign